Package: sconn
Title: Handles Spark connection to Databricks in R
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    c(
        person(
            "Fran", "Barton",
            email = "francis.barton@nhs.net",
            role = c("aut", "cre"),
            comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-5650-1176")
        ),
        person("The Strategy Unit", role = c("cph", "fnd"))
    )
Description: A very simple package that provides a function to connect to a
    Databricks instance, and a function to disconnect. The user should set up
    Databricks authentication details as environment variables, ideally in
    their `.Renviron` file.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
